description: "Bunga terung custom art mandala". the eggplant flower means that the Dayak people as nomads can live anywhere,” said the man whose long hair is turning white and knows a lot about the meaning behind tattoos. “Like eggplant seeds that are sown under any conditions, but can grow.Mandala is a complex abstract design that is usually circular in form.
